<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application><acronym>GNOME</acronym> Session</application></title>

<para>Installez <application><acronym>GNOME</acronym> Session</application> en lançant les commandes suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=`pkg-config --variable=prefix ORBit-2.0` \
    --localstatedir=/var/lib --sysconfdir=/etc/gnome  &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>

